Klopp on Can's contract: &quot;It's no secret how much I like Emre. He likes the club. We're in talks. There is no pressure. All is good.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp on Can: &quot;I am quite positive. Keeping good players makes sense and Emre is a good player.&quot;

@trentaa98: &quot;I&rsquo;d always try to find a crack in the wall so I could peep through to Melwood. It wasn&rsquo;t the best view of training!&quot;<br />
<br />
@trentaa98: &quot;Sometimes we used to drive past the entrance with my mum. Gerrard, Carragher, Alonso &amp; Torres were my heroes. I loved Alonso.&quot;<br />
<br />
@trentaa98: &quot;I always dreamed that one day I&rsquo;d be able to come through those gates as a Liverpool player. Thankfully, it&rsquo;s come true.&quot;<br />
<br />
@trentaa98 on Klopp: &quot;You can always go into his office &amp; ask him a question about what you need to improve on to make you a better player.<br />
<br />
@trentaa98: &quot;He puts his faith in you. If you go out there and repay that faith then he will always embrace you with a big hug.&quot;<br />
<br />
@trentaa98: &quot;I want to play for Liverpool for my whole career and one day hopefully I&rsquo;ll captain the side.&quot;
